parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's occupants are not provided with the necessary protection.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
airbag warning light illuminates
airbag warning light flashes on and off
no airbag deployment in a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbag sensors can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash or the unnecessary deployment of airbags, which can cause injuries or accidents.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates
airbag warning light flashes on and off
airbag sensor failure
airbag system malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unnecessarily, fail to deploy in a crash, or cause other safety issues, which can lead to injuries or accidents.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illuminates
airbag warning light flashes on and off
airbag system malfunction
airbag deployment failure
airbag failure to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries or fatalities to the driver, passengers, and pedestrians.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and uncontrollably
often when the brake pedal is applied
and may surge forward or lurch out of control
making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cruise control malfunction can cause the vehicle to accelerate suddenly and uncontrollably, leading to accidents and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The cruise control engages without input
and the vehicle accelerates rapidly
even when the brake pedal is applied
making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Throttle Body or Fuel Injector Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Throttle body or fuel injector issues can cause sudden acceleration, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, leading to accidents and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle surges forward or accelerates suddenly
often when the brake pedal is applied
and may experience intermittent acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal issues can cause the vehicle to accelerate suddenly and uncontrollably, leading to accidents and injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
and the vehicle accelerates suddenly
even when the brake pedal is applied
making it difficult or impossible to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension can cause the vehicle to vibrate, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates
makes loud clunking noises
and has a knocking sound coming from the rear suspension.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front suspension can cause the vehicle to vibrate, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates
makes loud crunching noises
and has a knocking sound coming from the front suspension.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the struts can cause the vehicle to vibrate, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates
makes loud clunking noises
and has a knocking sound coming from the struts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the strut mounts can cause the vehicle to vibrate, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates
makes loud crunching noises
and has a knocking sound coming from the strut mounts.
